      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> ginger</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop ﬁnely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
