          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the noodles are softening, combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> with 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp] </span>[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> – this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
