      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>outer</strong> <strong>lettuce leaves </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces and shred the<strong> inner core</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stalks and chop them roughly, discarding the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
