    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel your<strong> mango[es]</strong></p><p>Stand the <strong>mango[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>upright and very carefully slice the flesh away from the <strong>stone[s]</strong></p><p>Tip: If you feel resistance against your knife, it means you are hitting the stone</p><p>Chop the <strong>mango flesh</strong> into small bite-sized pieces, discarding the stone[s]</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
